g.text: M1 | virtual-memory-sim-m1 | Flat Page Table + Address Translation + Demand Paging
M2 | virtual-memory-sim-m2 | TLB + ASID + LRU/Random Eviction + Coherence
M3 | virtual-memory-sim-m3 | Multi-Level PT + CR3 + On-Demand Allocation + Overhead
M4 | virtual-memory-sim-m4 | Page Replacement: FIFO/LRU/Clock/Optimal + Swap
uint32_t pfn : 20 | Physical Frame Number — bits[31:12]
uint32_t referenced : 1 | A-bit — any access sets this
uint32_t dirty : 1 | D-bit — write access only
uint32_t valid : 1 | V-bit — Present in RAM
Total: 4 bytes | cache line holds 16 PTEs (64B / 4B)
uint32_t pt_addr : 20 | Phys base of 2nd-level PT — bits[31:12]
uint32_t vpn | Tag: Virtual Page Number — offset 0x00
uint32_t pfn | Data: Physical Frame Number — offset 0x04
uint16_t asid | Address Space ID — offset 0x08
Total: 12 bytes | 64-entry TLB = 768B fits in 32KB L1
uint64_t load_time | Logical timestamp of alloc (FIFO) — 0x08
uint64_t last_access | Logical timestamp of last use (LRU) — 0x10
Total: 32 bytes | 2 descriptors per 64B cache line
uint32_t vaddr | 32-bit virtual address from trace
